title: Turnbull ministry faces first parliamentary test with Abbott sitting on backbenches
text: Three weeks after being sworn in Malcolm Turnbull's reshuffled Federal Ministry are facing their first scrutiny in parliament. The former prime minister Tony Abbott is also expected to take up a seat on the backbench for the first time in two decades. ...
